pageProduct.name: Swisse Echinacea 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Echinacea is a premium quality formula to help support healthy immune system function and relieve symptoms of mild upper respiratory tract infections.

Immune Health: Echinacea supports a healthy immune system.

Mild Upper Respiratory Tract Infections: Echinacea is traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to relieve symptoms o mild upper respiratory tract infections.

Size: 60

Warnings

WARNINGS:

Vitamin & mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. For adult use only.

Ingredients

Each tablet contains:

ECHINACEA (Echinacea purpurea dry herb juice 133.33 mg) equiv. fresh herb juice 6g
Allergen information

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, artificial flavours or artificial colours.

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:

One tablet daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

STORAGE:

Store below 25°C. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
